     Are you ready for one of the sweetest Match 3 games ever made?!? In
     "Dessert Storm", you switch desserts in order to match lines of
     three or more. By doing so, the desserts subsequently disappear,
     and other desserts will form. Clear a dessert in every location on
     the board before the time runs out to win. The whole time you play
     an adorable little ice cream man is cheering you along.
     It comes with 21 puzzles with a delicious points and star system.
     Each time you play Ã‚â€” even if youÃ‚â€™re replaying the same puzzle Ã‚â€” the
     puzzle will be spawned completely different so you can play again
     and again. On top of this we have the just for fun Relax mode and a
     super exhilarating Rush mode that lets you play as long as you can
     last. The best thing of all is that instead of gaining calories you
     might actually be burning them by the time you are done!

     Features:

     - Beautiful graphics and delicious looking desserts in a game that
       the entire family can enjoy!
     - 21 different puzzle levels with each one never being quite the
       same.
     - Delicious point and star system designed to help keep you focused.
     - High speed Rush mode where the limit is your dessert matching
       skills!
     - A nice Relax mode to help you learn and wind down at the end of a
       long day.
     - Super happy music and fun sounds
